pan>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"659211cb6858aff2911b40cba4b3ff4f72736194","tid":1535192,"uid":24845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"自己諗"},{"pid":"ab01f6dca0a0845627d28b421ef74d9a023b33bb","tid":1535192,"uid":24845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:43:10.000Z","msg":"自己諗"},{"pid":"594a8e6cbe84b78ec70a22e9f79ded8c4caf9e58","tid":1535192,"uid":100772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:47:33.000Z","msg":"打唔打都拉你"}]}